node.text: Had the best time launching my very own “LIANE” Ponytail with one of my fave brands @insertnamehere 💕 Also being able to work with amazing talented people, and see my vision come to life is so unreal! I love and enjoy every second of it! And I’m able to do all this because of YOU! My supporters and motivators! I appreciate and love you all so much! 🥺You keep me going! 👏🏽😘 Stay tuned for more fun projects like this! Can’t wait to share what I have planned for 2021 😏🎉

node.text: Visiting Dubai has definitely put my mindset on a new level. Everything is so futuristic here 😍 It’s blown my mind that a lot of this is man made. It shows how capable we are to build and manifest amazing things in our lives simply by setting our minds to it. You can rise up from anything. You can shift and elevate the way you think. You can recreate yourself and your circumstances exactly how you envision it. Nothing is ever final. The possibilities are endless 🤍

node.text:
I’m completely overwhelmed with so much love and gratefulness.🌹Wish I could explain the happiness I feel! 🥰 Your support and uplifting words bring tears to my eyes. I read your comments, your DM’s, and feel extremely blessed to be able to connect with my followers like this. I’ve opened up my life and allowed myself to become vulnerable with all of you with my relationship with @donbenjamin. 
It wasn’t easy, but sharing my story and all the ups and downs have only brought me closer to all of you. And that I’m not alone, there’s many of you that have experienced the same things I have and shared your own personal stories with me. Thank you for that. I cherish and appreciate all your support from the bottom of my heart. ❤️ God bless you all! 🙏🏽

node.text:
So this happened 😭💍❤️
Since I was a little girl, I’ve always loved watching romance and Disney movies. The princess always found love and lived happily ever after. It painted a picture of what love should look like. But what I’ve learned through the years. Love isn’t just a perfect fairytale. Relationships don’t last because of the good times; they last because the hard times were handled with love, communication, hard work, forgiveness, patience, and understanding. Me and Don have been through a series of ups and downs. We’ve broken up before and took our space apart, worked on ourselves and somehow God brought us back together. Better, wiser, and stronger. ❤️‍🔥
Love is a partnership. Love is supposed to bring the best out of each other. I knew in my heart, what was meant to be, will happen. My faith and focus in God, my self love, and growth have somehow brought me back to him. I do believe people can change for the better, but they have to want it and do the work for themselves. Because I’m definitely not the same person I was last year. And the past year I’ve also seen Don transform to become the man I’ve always believed he could be. Our bond has grown so much stronger through this journey. We were put on earth to evolve, grow, and learn from our past. And not falling in love with your partner, but RISING in LOVE. We are moving with purpose. 🔥🙏🏽❤️ Thank you to everyone who has been a part of this journey! This is just the beginning of a beautiful chapter🌹 
Watch our new @foreverus YouTube video NOW about this special proposal 💍😍
